PERSONALIZED
SOLUTIONS

truly tailored experience
• Templating allows the surgeon to determine implant size in
advance; this is designed toresult in fewer implants and
instruments, with a goal to increase operating room eciencies
• Personalized positioning guides streamline total knee replacement
surgery & reduce instrumentation by ensuring reproducible guide
fixation
• iASSIST® alignment technology helps the surgeon align implants
to each patient’s unique anatomy without pre-operative imaging
